<div id="txtcont" class="span9" style="position: relative;">
    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='221:248'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '015-1a' );" name="015-1a" class="pb">[015-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='248:261'>禮記要義卷第十六　大傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='261:276'>　一王者諸侯大夫士禘祫之尊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='276:296'>禮不王不禘王者禘其祖之所自出以其祖配</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='296:316'>之諸侯及其大祖大夫士有大事省於其君干</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='316:336'>祫及其髙祖注云凡大祭曰禘自由也大祭其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='336:356'>先祖所由生謂郊祀天也太祖受封君也大事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='356:376'>㓂戍之事也省善也善於其君謂免於大難也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='376:393'>于猶空也空祫謂無廟祫祭之於壇墠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='393:402'>　二武王柴祈奠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='402:429'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '015-1b' );" name="015-1b" class="pb">[015-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='429:449'>牧之野武王之大事也旣事而退柴於上帝祈</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='449:469'>於社設奠於牧室注云柴祈奠告天地及先祖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='469:489'>也牧室牧野之室也古者郊關皆有館焉先祖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='489:495'>者行主也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='495:514'>　三追王不以卑臨尊然亦有不必追王者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='514:534'>追王大王亶父王季歴文王昌不以卑臨尊也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='534:554'>注云不用諸侯之號臨天子也文王稱王早矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='554:574'>於殷猶爲諸侯於是著焉正義曰案此武王追</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='574:594'>王大王亶父王季歴文王昌案合符后云文王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='594:621'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '015-2a' );" name="015-2a" class="pb">[015-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='621:641'>立后稷配天追王大王亶甫王季歴與此不同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='641:661'>者文王暫追王耳號謚未定至武王時乃定之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='661:681'>矣中庸云周公追王大王王季者謂以王禮改</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='681:701'>葬耳不改葬文王者先以王禮葬故也此大王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='701:721'>王季追王者王迹所由興故追王也所以追王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='721:741'>者以子爲天子而不以卑臨尊若非王迹所由</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='741:761'>不必追王也故小記云父爲士子爲天子諸侯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='761:781'>祭以天子諸侯其尸服以士服是也周語云先</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='781:801'>王不窋武成云先王建邦啓土謂后稷皆稱先</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='801:828'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '015-2b' );" name="015-2b" class="pb">[015-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='828:848'>王者以王者之先祖故通稱先王也契稱玄王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='848:854'>與此同矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='854:866'>　五賜姓賜氏賜族之別</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='866:886'>凡姓族異者所以別異人也猶萬物皆各有名</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='886:906'>以相分別天子賜姓賜氏諸侯但賜氏不得賜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='906:926'>姓降於天子也故隱八年左傳云無駭卒公問</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='926:946'>族於衆仲衆仲對曰天子建德因生以賜姓胙</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='946:966'>之土而命之氏諸侯以字爲謚因以爲族官有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='966:986'>丗功則有官族邑亦如之以此言之天子因諸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='986:1013'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '015-3a' );" name="015-3a" class="pb">[015-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1013:1033'>侯先祖所生賜之曰姓杜預云若舜生嬀汭賜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1033:1053'>姓曰嬀封舜之後於陳以所封之土命爲氏舜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1053:1073'>後姓嬀而氏曰陳故鄭駮異義云炎帝姓姜大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1073:1093'>皡之所賜也黃帝姓姬炎帝之所賜也故堯賜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1093:1113'>伯夷姓曰姜賜禹姓曰姒賜契姓曰子賜稷姓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1113:1133'>曰姬著在書傳如鄭此言是天子賜姓也諸侯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1133:1153'>賜卿大夫以氏若同姓公之子曰公子公子之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1153:1173'>子曰公孫公孫之子其親巳逺不得上連於公</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1173:1193'>故以王父字爲氏若適夫人之子則以五十字</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1193:1220'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '015-3b' );" name="015-3b" class="pb">[015-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1220:1240'>伯仲爲氏若魯之仲孫季孫是也若庶子妾子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1240:1260'>則以二十字爲氏則展氏臧氏是也若異姓則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1260:1280'>以父祖官及所食之邑爲氏以官爲氏者則司</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1280:1300'>馬司城是也以邑爲氏者若韓趙魏是也凡賜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1300:1320'>氏族者此爲卿乃賜有大功德者生賜以族若</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1320:1340'>叔孫得臣是也雖公子之身若有大功德則以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1340:1360'>公子之字賜以爲族若仲遂是也其無功徳死</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1360:1380'>後乃賜族若無駭是也若子孫不爲卿其君不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1380:1400'>賜族子孫自以王父字爲族也氏族對之爲別</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1400:1427'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '015-4a' );" name="015-4a" class="pb">[015-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1427:1447'>散則通也故左傳云問族於衆仲下云公命以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1447:1467'>字爲展氏是也其姓與氏散亦得通故春秋有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1467:1482'>姜氏子氏姜子皆姓而云氏是也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1482:1497'>　六弟妻亦謂之婦嫂不謂之母</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1497:1517'>凡子行之妻乃謂之爲婦弟非子行其妻亦謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1517:1537'>之婦者以兄弟同倫嫌相褻瀆弟雖非子行其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1537:1557'>妻同子行之妻謂之爲婦欲卑逺之弟妻旣得</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1557:1577'>爲婦號記者恐兄妻得爲母號故記者明之云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1577:1597'>是嫂亦可謂之母乎言嫂不可亦謂之爲母也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1597:1624'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '015-4b' );" name="015-4b" class="pb">[015-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1624:1639'>　七姓丗所由生有正姓有庶姓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1639:1659'>四丗而緦服之窮也五丗袒免殺同姓也六丗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1659:1679'>親屬竭矣其庶姓別於上而戚單於下昏姻可</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1679:1699'>以通乎繫之以姓而弗別綴之以食而弗殊雖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1699:1719'>百丗而昬姻不通者周道然也注云四丗共髙</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1719:1739'>祖五丗髙祖昆弟六丗以外親盡無屬名通乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1739:1759'>問之也玄孫之子姓別於髙祖五丗而無服姓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1759:1779'>丗所由生周之禮所建者長也姓正姓也始祖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1779:1799'>爲正姓髙祖爲庶姓繫之弗別謂若今宗室屬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1799:1826'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '015-5a' );" name="015-5a" class="pb">[015-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1826:1846'>籍也周禮小史掌定繫丗辨昭穆正義曰玄孫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='1846:1866'>與髙祖服屬仍同其姓與髙祖不異玄孫之子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='1866:1886'>則從兄弟承髙祖父之後至已五丗而無服各</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='1886:1906'>事小宗因字因官爲氏不同髙祖之父是庶姓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='1906:1926'>別於上庶姓爲衆姓也則氏族之謂也云姓丗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='1926:1946'>所由生者據五丗無服不相禀承各爲氏姓繫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='1946:1966'>之以姓而弗別者周法雖庶姓別於上而有丗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='1966:1986'>繫連繫之以本姓而不分別若姬氏姜氏大宗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='1986:2006'>百丗不改也姓正姓者對氏族爲正姓也云始</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='2006:2033'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '015-5b' );" name="015-5b" class="pb">[015-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='2033:2053'>祖爲正姓者若炎帝姓姜黃帝姓姬周姓姬本</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='2053:2073'>於黃帝齊姓姜本於炎帝宋姓子本於契是始</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='2073:2093'>祖爲正姓也云髙祖爲庶姓者若魯之三桓慶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='2093:2113'>父叔牙季友之後及鄭之七穆子游子國之後</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='2113:2122'>爲游氏國氏之等</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='2122:2129'>八服術有六</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2129:2149'>服術有六一曰親親二曰尊尊三曰名四曰出</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2149:2169'>入五曰長㓜六曰從服注云術猶道也親親父</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2169:2189'>母爲首尊尊君爲首名丗母叔母之屬也出入</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2189:2216'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '015-6a' );" name="015-6a" class="pb">[015-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2216:2236'>女子子嫁者及在室者長㓜成人及殤也從服</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2236:2251'>若夫爲妻之父母妻爲夫之黨服</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2251:2258'>九從服有六</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2258:2278'>從服有六有屬從有徒從有從有服而無服有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2278:2298'>從無服而有服有從重而輕有從輕而重注云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2298:2318'>子爲母之黨臣爲君之黨公子爲其妻之父母</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2318:2338'>公子之妻爲公子之外兄弟夫爲妻之父母公</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2338:2347'>子之妻爲其皇姑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2347:2357'>　十別子繼別繼禰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2357:2384'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '015-6b' );" name="015-6b" class="pb">[015-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2384:2404'>別子爲祖繼別爲宗繼禰者爲小宗注云別子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2404:2424'>謂公子若始來在此國者後丗以爲祖也別子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2424:2444'>之丗適也族人尊之謂之大宗是宗子也父之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2444:2456'>適也兄弟尊之謂之小宗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2456:2467'><span class='krp-note'>十/一</span>大宗小宗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2467:2487'>有百丗不遷之宗有五丗則遷之宗百丗不遷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2487:2507'>者別子之後也宗其繼別子之所自出者百丗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2507:2527'>不遷者也宗其繼髙祖者五丗則遷者也尊祖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2527:2547'>故敬宗敬宗尊祖之義也注云遷猶變易也繼</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2547:2574'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '015-7a' );" name="015-7a" class="pb">[015-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2574:2594'>别子别子之丗適也繼髙祖者亦小宗也先言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='2594:2614'>繼禰者據别子子弟之子也以髙祖與禰皆有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='2614:2634'>繼者則曽祖亦有也則小宗四與大宗凡五正</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='2634:2654'>義曰云有百丗不遷之宗者謂大宗也云有五</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='2654:2674'>丗則遷之宗者謂小宗也云百丗不遷者别子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='2674:2694'>之後也宗有繼别子之所自出者百丗不遷者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='2694:2714'>也此覆明大宗子百丗不遷之義也云宗其繼</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='2714:2734'>髙祖者五丗則遷者也此覆明小宗子五丗則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='2734:2754'>遷之義云尊祖故敬宗敬宗尊祖之義也者此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='2754:2781'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '015-7b' );" name="015-7b" class="pb">[015-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='2781:2801'>揔結大宗小宗以大宗是逺祖之正體小宗是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='2801:2821'>髙祖之正體尊崇其祖故敬宗子小宗四與大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='2821:2841'>宗凡五者小宗四謂一是繼禰與親兄弟爲宗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='2841:2861'>二是繼祖與同堂兄弟爲宗三是繼曽祖與再</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='2861:2881'>從兄弟爲宗四是繼髙祖與三從兄弟爲宗是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='2881:2897'>小宗四并繼別子之大宗凡五宗也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='2897:2914'><span class='krp-note'>十/二</span>宗適如大宗宗庶如小宗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='2914:2934'>公子有宗道公子之公爲其士大夫之庶者宗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='2934:2954'>其士大夫之適者公子之宗道也注云公子不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='2954:2981'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '015-8a' );" name="015-8a" class="pb">[015-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='2981:3001'>得宗君君命適昆弟爲之宗使之宗之是公子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='3001:3021'>之宗道也所宗者適則如大宗死爲之齊衰九</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='3021:3041'>月其母則小君也爲其妻齊衰三月無適而宗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='3041:3061'>庶則如小宗死爲之大功九月其母妻無服公</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='3061:3076'>子唯已而巳則無所宗亦莫之宗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='3076:3096'><span class='krp-note'>十/三</span>同髙祖者緦麻族屬絶則無移服</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='3096:3117'>絶族無移服注族昆弟之子不相爲服正文親者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='3117:3137'>屬也注有親者服各以其屬親䟽正義曰此一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='3137:3157'>節論親盡則無服有親則有服絶族者謂三從</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='3157:3184'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '015-8b' );" name="015-8b" class="pb">[015-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='3184:3204'>兄弟同髙祖者族兄弟緦麻族兄弟之子及四</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='3204:3224'>從兄弟爲族屬旣絶故無移服在旁而及曰移</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='3224:3232'>言不延移及之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='3232:3253'><span class='krp-note'>十/四</span>不顯不承鄭詩禮注異以注有先後</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='3253:3273'>詩云不顯不承無斁於人斯此之謂也斁厭也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='3273:3293'>言文王之德不顯乎不承成先人之業乎言其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='3293:3313'>顯且承之人樂之無厭也正義曰詩箋云周公</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='3313:3333'>祭清廟是不光明文王之德與言其光明之也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='3333:3353'>是不承順文王志意與言其承順之也與此注</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='3353:3380'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '015-9a' );" name="015-9a" class="pb">[015-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='3380:3400'>不同者禮注在前詩箋在後故詩有與禮注不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='3400:3411'>同故鄭荅炅模云然也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='3411:3421'>禮記要義卷第十六</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='3421:3448'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '015-9b' );" name="015-9b" class="pb">[015-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
